Source: Otago Witness
Author:
Vol / Page: 57
Edition:
Quote: My father was camped at Breakfast Creek, and I helped him to shift along the beach to the mouth of the Waiau River, and when coming along the beach with the horse and dray we got stuck in a quicksand, but we got out after a lot of trouble.
